  • Constructor Details

    • AppUI

      public AppUI​(net.rgielen.fxweaver.core.FxWeaver weaver, org.springframework.context.ConfigurableApplicationContext ctx)

      Constructs a new AppUI instance.

      Details

      1. The AppUI is constructed as an injected singleton Spring Component.
      2. Both FxWeaver and ApplicationContext parameters are Autowired.
      Parameters:
      weaver - The autowired FxWeaver variable for this Springable object.
      ctx - The autowired ApplicationContext variable for this Springable object.

  • Method Details

    • init

      protected void init()

      Initializes this AppUI.

      Initialization Process

      1. Initializes the singleton Console object.
      2. Sets the contentManager of this AppUI to a new ContentManager.
        • The Content Stack Pane of this AppUI is used as the Content Base for the constructed ContentManager object.
      3. Sets the content of the constructed ContentManager to a new TestContent.
        • This AppUI instance is used only to pass its Springable values to the constructed TestContent.
